Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20during%20his%20ongoing%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Ambikapur%20announced%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20has%20decided%20to%20give%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20MSP%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20in%20the%20country%20are%20not%20getting%20what%20they%20should%20get.%20Farmers%20are%20marching%20to%20Delhi%20but%20they%20are%20being%20stopped%2C%20tear%20gas%20shells%20are%20being%20fired%20on%20them%20and%20they%20are%20being%20jailed.%20What%20are%20the%20farmers%20saying%3F%20Just%20that%20we%20should%20get%20the%20fruits%20of%20our%20hard%20work.%20The%20BJP%20gave%20Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20M.S.%20Swaminathan.%20But%20the%20cause%20to%20which%20Swaminathan%20devoted%20his%20life%2C%20his%20recommendations%20on%20MSP%2C%20they%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20do.%20Swaminathan%20report%20clearly%20said%20that%20farmers%20should%20get%20MSP%20as%20a%20legal%20right.%20But%20BJP%20is%20not%20doing%20this.%20If%20INDIA%20alliance%20forms%20the%20government%20we%20will%20give%20MSP%E2%80%99s%20legal%20guarantee%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20while%20addressing%20a%20public%20gathering.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Randeep%20Singh%20Surjewala%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20will%20be%20remembered%20in%20history%20for%20its%20%E2%80%9Ccruelty%2C%20barbarity%2C%20repression%20and%20oppression%20against%20farmers%E2%80%9D%20and%20questioned%20why%20they%20are%20being%20stopped%20from%20coming%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20history%20is%20written%2C%20the%2010-year%20tenure%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20will%20be%20known%20as%20the%20period%20of%20cruelty%2C%20barbarity%2C%20repression%20and%20oppression%20against%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20suppress%20the%20voice%20of%20farmers%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20converted%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20capital%20Delhi%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98police%20cantonment%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20if%20an%20enemy%20has%20attacked%20the%20power%20in%20Delhi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHeavy%20security%20has%20been%20deployed%20along%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20borders%20including%20barricades%20and%20barbed%20wire.%20Prohibitory%20orders%20under%20Section%20144%20have%20also%20been%20imposed%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Haryana%20police%20fired%20tear%20gas%20shells%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20border%20between%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%2C%20as%20farmers%20broke%20barricades%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20continue%20their%20march.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20call%20was%20given%20by%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%20and%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(non-political)%20led%20by%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20and%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%2C%20respectively%2C%20and%20other%20unions%20demanding%20for%20a%20law%20on%20the%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%2C%20withdrawing%20criminal%20cases%20filed%20during%20the%202020%20farm%20protest%2C%20a%20farm%20loan%20waiver%20among%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ftalks-with-union-ministers-inconclusive-farmers-stick-with-plan-to-march-to-delhi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emeeting%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ebetween%20Union%20ministers%20and%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leaders%20held%20on%20Monday%20to%20prevent%20a%202020-21%20like%20agitation%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20failed%20to%20yield%20a%20consensus%20with%20the%20farmers%20deciding%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20their%20march%20to%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarl