d.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Central%20Government%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20support%20farmers%20and%20labourers%2C%20coupled%20with%20futile%20PR%20stunts%2C%20exposes%20the%20illusion%20of%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat.%E2%80%99%20Instead%20of%20suppressing%20their%20protest%2C%20BJP%20must%20focus%20on%20humbling%20their%20inflated%20egos%2C%20power-hungry%20ambitions%2C%20and%20inadequate%20governance%20that%20has%20harmed%20our%20nation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20in%20Delhi%2C%20earlier%20on%20Tuesday%20denied%20permission%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20convert%20the%20Bawana%20stadium%20into%20a%20temporary%20jail%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20letter%20from%20Delhi%20home%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20demands%20are%20%E2%80%9Cgenuine%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20every%20citizen%20has%20the%20Constitutional%20right%20to%20protest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAAP%E2%80%99s%20new%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Swati%20Maliwal%20has%20also%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20Modi%20urging%20him%20to%20%E2%80%9Cpersonally%20intervene%E2%80%9D%20and%20lend%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccompassionate%20ear%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20demands.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20recent%20recognition%20of%20Shri%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20and%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20has%20brought%20a%20moment%20of%20pride%20for%20our%20agricultural%20community.%20However%20%2C%20it%20is%20disheartening%20to%20witness%20the%20same%20community%20now%20facing%20tear%20gas%20and%20impediments%20on%20their%20journey%20to%20secure%20their%20rightful%20demands%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBJP%3A%20Annadata%20Samman%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20remained%20steadfast%20in%20its%20commitment%20to%20farmers%20through%20its%20policies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAlong%20with%20Nari%20Shakti%2C%20Yuva%20Shakti%2C%20Annadatas%20have%20been%20the%20pillar%20for%20which%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20been%20working%20for%20in%20a%20steadfast%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shazia%20Ilmi%2C%20national%20spokesperson%2C%20BJP%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20implemented%20policies%20for%20farmers%20benefits%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20giving%20health%20cards%2C%20provision%20of%20loans%20at%20low%20interests%20or%20samman%20rashi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20promise%20to%20legalise%20MSP%2C%20Ilmi%20questioned%20why%20the%20party%20had%20not%20implemented%20it%20earlier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20posted%20multiple%20times%20on%20its%20X%20account%2C%20highlighting%20how%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20been%20empowering%20farmers%20through%20its%20schemes%20with%20the%20hashtag%20AnnadataKaSamman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20government%20is%20fully%20committed%20to%20providing%20100%20percent%20benefits%20of%20the%20schemes%20to%20the%20farmer%20brothers%20and%20sisters%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20one%20post.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20series%20of%20posts%2C%20it%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20increased%20the%20MSP%20on%20wheat%2C%20barley%2C%20masoor%2C%20channa%20among%20others%20in%20comparison%20to%20what%20was%20being%20provided%20prior%20to%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20another%20post%2C%20the%20BJP%20said%20that%20farmers%20had%20become%20%E2%80%9Cself-reliant%20due%20to%20increase%20in%20food%20production%20capacity%20during%20the%20Modi%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1