%20order%20to%20be%20eligible%20for%20the%20cash-rich%20league's%20lucrative%20auction%20pool.%20It%20has%20been%20learnt%20that%20BCCI%20brass%20has%20already%20instructed%20Kishan%20to%20play%20Jharkhand's%20last%20group%20league%20game%20against%20Rajasthan%20in%20Jamshedpur%2C%20starting%20February%2016.%20The%20manner%20in%20which%20Kishan%20had%20skipped%20match%20after%20match%20after%20returning%20midway%20from%20South%20Africa%20tour%20citing%20%26quot%3Btravel%20fatigue%26quot%3B%20hasn't%20exactly%20gone%20down%20well%20with%20men%20who%20matter%20in%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20so%20after%20it%20was%20found%20that%20he%20is%20training%20in%20Baroda%20with%20his%20new%20MI%20skipper%20Hardik%20Pandya%20while%20his%20state%20team%20is%20languishing%20near%20bottom%20of%20group%20A%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20general%20consensus%20that%20a%20strict%20policy%20need%20to%20be%20adhered%20to%20so%20that%20a%20group%20of%20young%20players%20don't%20make%20%26quot%3Bplaying%20IPL%20to%20IPL%26quot%3B%20a%20habit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20makers%20in%20BCCI%20are%20well%20aware%20that%20some%20players%20don't%20want%20to%20play%20any%20red%20ball%20cricket.%20If%20they%20are%20out%20of%20Indian%20team%2C%20they%20would%20at%20best%20play%20a%20few%20Mushtaq%20Ali%20T20%20games%20and%20then%20not%20report%20for%20state%20team%20duty%20during%20red%20ball%20season%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20BCCI%20official%20told%20PTI%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20rein%20in%20such%20players%2C%20board%20in%20all%20likelihood%20will%20make%20it%20mandatory%20to%20play%203-4%20Ranji%20Trophy%20games%2C%20failing%20which%2C%20they%20can't%20play%20IPL%20or%20even%20appear%20in%20IPL%20auction%20if%20released%20by%20their%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20units%20feel%20unless%20the%20diktat%20comes%20from%20top%20of%20BCCI%2C%20some%20of%20the%20young%20stars%20will%20treat%20Ranji%20Trophy%20with%20disdain.%26quot%3B%20It%20is%20understood%20that%20even%20Indian%20team's%20think-tank%20are%20pissed%20off%20with%20a%20certain%20section%20of%20players%2C%20who%20are%20always%20reluctant%20to%20play%20Ranji%20Trophy%20even%20when%20they%20are%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20understand%20Hardik%20Pandya's%20case%20as%20his%20body%20can't%20take%20the%20rigours%20of%20red%20ball%20cricket.%20He%20can't%20withstand%20the%20workload%20of%20Test%20cricket%20and%20India%20needs%20him%20fit%20for%20ICC%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20some%20of%20the%20other%20youngsters%2C%20whenever%20you%20call%20them%2C%20they%20will%20cite%20that%20they%20are%20currently%20doing%20physio%20work.%20There%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20stop%20somewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20find%20out%20if%20Kishan%20finally%20leaves%20his%20%26quot%3Bnew%20training%20base%26quot%3B%20in%20Baroda%20and%20is%20back%20in%20Jamshedpur%20for%20Jharkhand's%20final%20game%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20Kishan%20would%20find%20himself%20out%20of%20BCCI%20retainership%20(he%20has%20a%20grade%20C%20annual%20contract%20of%20Rs%201%20crore)%2C%20the%20official%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%20discussions%20have%20taken%20place%20as%20of%20now%20regarding%20central%20contracts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707829500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fr2363d8g_ishan-kishan_625x300_02_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fno-ranji-trophy-no-ipl-after-ishan-kishan-fiasco-bcci-takes-stern-step-report-5050576%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ishan%20Kishan's%20reluctance%20to%20play%20first-class%20cricket%20could%20prompt%20the%20BCCI%20to%20make%20a%20minimum%20number%20of%20Ranji%20Trophy%20games%20mandatory%20in%20order%20to%20be%20eligible%20for%20IPL.%22%2C%22a