C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcop28-dubai-un-climate-conference-pm-modi-in-dubai-for-cop28-as-200-nations-reach-historic-climate-agreement-4623038%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520his%2520statement%252C%2520PM%2520Modi%2Cglobal%2520emissions%2520continue%2520to%2520surge.%5C%22%3Ein%20December%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20he%20participated%20in%20the%20United%20Nations%20Framework%20Convention%20on%20the%20Climate%20Change%20(UNFCCC)%20Conference%20of%20Parties%20(COP28)%20Climate%20Summit%20hosted%20by%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20inaugurating%20the%20BAPS%20temple%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20be%20addressing%20the%20Indian%20community%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fover-65-000-register-for-pms-ahlan-modi-event-in-abu-dhabi-5045620%5C%22%3E'Ahlan%20Modi'%20event%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20Sheikh%20Zayed%20Stadium.%20Several%20agreements%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20be%20signed%20during%20the%20visit.%20The%20engagement%20with%20the%20UAE%20started%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Modi%20government's%20strategy%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20worldwide.%20Since%20remittances%20from%20the%20Gulf%20countries%20form%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20total%20remittance%20flows%20into%20India%2C%20PM%20Modi's%20first%20visit%20to%20UAE%20in%202015%20had%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20an%20expansive%20bilateral%20engagement%20that%20has%20acquired%20multilateral%20dimensions%20today.%20On%20January%2010%20this%20year%2C%20UAE%20President%20Mohamed%20bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan%20visited%20India%20as%20the%20chief%20guest%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvibrant-gujarat-summit-pm-modi-warm-welcome-uae-president-mohammed-bin-zayed-al-nahyan-4831074%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPM%2520Modi%2520and%2520the%2520UAE%2CUAE%2520leader%2520on%2520his%2520arrival.%5C%22%3E'Vibrant%20Gujarat%20Summit'%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Gandhinagar%20and%20made%20a%20rare%20speech.%20Earlier%2C%20in%202017%2C%20the%20UAE%20President%20had%20been%20in%20India%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3E-8hZEp8Yo%5C%22%3Echief%20guest%20for%20the%20Republic%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20as%20a%20special%20invitee%20for%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20leaderships%20of%20both%20the%20countries%20have%20taken%20several%20initiatives%20to%20treat%20each%20other%20as%20equal%20partners%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20the%20India-UAE%20relationship%20has%20made%20significant%20strides.%20Both%20countries%20have%20reaffirmed%2C%20at%20regional%20and%20international%20levels%2C%20their%20joint%20commitment%20to%20combat%20extremism%20and%20terrorism%2C%20including%20cross-border%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhy%20The%20Temple%20Is%20An%20Achievement%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20indeed%20an%20achievement%20that%20the%20UAE%2C%20an%20Islamic%20emirate%2C%20has%20allowed%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20biggest%20Hindu%20temple%20outside%20India.%20The%20foundation%20for%20the%20first%20traditional%20BAPS%20Hindu%20Mandir%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20was%20laid%20on%20April%2020%2C%202019.%20Later%2C%20in%20May%202023%2C%20diplomats%20from%20over%2030%20countries%20visited%20the%20under-construction%20site.%20The%2027-acre%20land%20for%20the%20BAPS%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20was%20donated%20by%20the%20UAE%20President.%20The%20temple%20itself%2C%20which%20has%20seven%20tall%20towers%2C%20each%20representing%20the%20seven%20emirates%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20is%20a%20unique%20blend%20of%20Indian%20culture%20and%20the%20UAE's%20identity.%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%20it%20is%20a%20home%20away%20from%20home.%20As%20a%20devout%20Hindu%2C%20I%20feel%20I%20get%20to%20practise%20every%20bit%20of%20my%20rituals%20with%20ease.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20new%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20and%20the%20existing%20temple%20in%20the%20Jebel%20Ali%20area%20of%20Dubai%20is%20icing%20on%20the%20cake%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Debjani%20Ghoshal%2C%20an%20educator%20who%20has%20been%20based%20in%20the%20UAE%20for%20five%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20community%20in%20the%20UAE%20has%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20its%20economic%20development.%20The%20Indian%20diaspora%20there%20is%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20Indians%20constitute%20about%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20UAE's%20population.%20The%20community%20is%20known%20for%20its%20competence%20and%20work%20culture.%20And%20because%20of%20these%20positives%2C%20Indian%20expatriates%20are%20well-respected%20in%20the%20UAE.%20%26quot%3BThanks%20to%20both%20the%20leaders%2C%20mutual%20respect%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20has%20benefited%20the%20Indian%20community%20immensely%2C%20right%20from%20a%20businessman%20to%20a%20skilled%20professional%2C%26quot%3B%20adds%20Ghoshal.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EA%20Huge%20Transformation%20In%20Ties%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PM%20Modi%20at%20the%20helm%2C%20bilateral%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UAE%20have%20undergone%20a%20transformation%2C%20both%20qualitatively%20and%20quantitatively.%20According%20to%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20data%2C%20India%20and%20the%20UAE%20are%20among%20each%20other's%20top%20trading%20partners%2C%20with%20a%20bilateral%20trade%20of%20about%20%2485%20billion%20in%202022-23%2C%20marking%20a%20year-on-year%20increase%20of%2016%25.%20Indian%20exports%20to%20the%20UAE%20have%20also%20recorded%20remarkable%20growth%2C%20reaching%20%2431.6%20billion%2C%20a%2012%25%20increase%20over%20the%20previous%20year.%20The%20UAE%20was%20among%20the%20top%20four%20investors%20in%20India%20in%20terms%20of%20foreign%20direct%20investments%20in%202022-23.%20India%20also%20stands%20to%20benefit%20a%20great%20deal%20from%20the%20UAE's%20focus%20on%20hydrocarbons%20and%20green%20energy.%20During%20his%20last%20meeting%20with%20the%20UAE%20President%2C%20which%20was%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20COP28%20conference%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20discussed%20various%20bilateral%20issues%20and%20both%20the%20countries%20collaborated%20closely%20on%20addressing%20the%20global%20challenge%20of%20climate%20change%20and%20enhancing%20cooperation%20on%20climate%20action%2C%20decarbonisation%2C%20and%20clean%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20bilateral%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UAE%20have%20evolved%20into%20a%20comprehensive%20strategic%20partnership%20today.%20Both%20countries%20signed%20a%20Comprehensive%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement%20(CEPA)%20in%20February%202022%20and%20initiated%20a%20Local%20Currency%20Settlement%20(LCS)%20System%20in%20July%202023%20to%20promote%20the%20use%20of%20Indian%20rupee%20and%20the%20AED%20(United%20Arab%20Emirates%20dirham)%20for%20cross-border%20transactions.%20The%20CEPA%20eliminates%20duties%20on%20many%20tariff%20lines%20and%20covers%20various%20sectors%2C%20benefiting%20industries%20like%20oil%20seeds%2C%20beverages%2C%20textiles%2C%20and%20pharmaceuticals.%20The%20BRICS%20summit%20in%20August%202023%2C%20during%20which%20the%20UAE%20joined%20the%20grouping%2C%20and%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20India-Middle%20East%20Economic%20Corridor%20(IMEEC)%20in%20New%20Delhi%20during%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20September%2C%20are%20a%20few%20other%20key%20pointers%20on%20the%20high%20level%20of%20cooperation.%20While%20the%20UAE's%20inclusion%20in%20the%20G20%20during%20India's%20presidency%20may%20be%20a%20strategic%20step%20forward%2C%20it%20has%20also%20strengthened%20the%20UAE's%20global%20and%20economic%20standing.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20proposed%20IMEEC%2C%20consisting%20of%20an%20eastern%20corridor%2C%20will%20connect%20India%20to%20the%20Gulf%20region%2C%20and%20a%20northern%20corridor%20will%20connect%20the%20Gulf%20region%20to%20Europe.%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20relationship%20has%20moved%20from%20a%20transactional%20to%20a%20comprehensive%20strategic%20partnership%2C%20with%20space%2C%20cyber%2C%20nuclear%2C%20defence%20and%20security%20getting%20greater%20importance%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ambassador%20(Retd)%20Anil%20Trigunayat%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20inauguration%20%26quot%3Bof%20the%20biggest%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20UAE's%20respect%20for%20Indians%20and%20their%20connected%20cultural%20heritage%2C%20as%20well%20as%20their%20policy%20of%20respect%20for%20all%20religions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Qatar%20Win%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20growing%20international%20might%20in%20the%20Gulf%20Cooperation%20Council%20(GCC)%20countries%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20countering%20radical%20Islamists%20and%20their%20handlers%20from%20across%20the%20border.%20That%20might%20was%20also%20a%20key%20factor%20in%20the%20recent%20release%20of%20the%20eight%20former%20Indian%20Navy%20personnel%20from%20Qatar%20on%20February%2012.%20The%20Indian%20government's%20frantic%20diplomatic%20efforts%20led%20to%20the%20commutation%20of%20the%20capital%20punishment%20to%20extended%20prison%20terms%20for%20the%20eight%20veterans%2C%20and%20ultimately%20their%20release.%20As%20a%20token%20of%20appreciation%20and%20to%20boost%20ties%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20also%20travel%20to%20Doha%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20Qatar%2C%20after%20concluding%20his%20two-day%20visit%20to%20the%20UAE.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20political%20landscape%20often%20sees%20temple%20politics%20taking%20the%20centre%20stage.%20Against%20that%2C%C2%A0the%20BAPS%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20is%20a%20symbolic%20reiteration%20of%20India's%20close%20ties%20with%20the%20UAE%20and%20a%20great%20example%20of%20the%20latter's%20values%20of%20tolerance%20and%20acceptance%20of%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707828780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F14aj9kao_pm-modi-uae-president_625x300_13_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Funder-pm-modi-india-uae-ties-are-at-an-all-time-high-5050639%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20started%20as%20bilateral%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UAE%20have%20evolved%20into%20a%20comprehensive%20strategic%20partnership%20today%2C%20whose%20strength%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20will%20be%20PM%20Modi's%20seventh%20visit%20to%20the%20country%20since%20August%202015.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Funder-pm-modi-india-uae-ties-are-at-an-all-time-high-5050639%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Funder-pm-modi-india-uae-ties-are-at-an-all-time-high-5050639%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Funder-pm-modi-india-uae-ties-are-at-an-all-time-high-5050639%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Four%20Armenian%20soldiers%20killed%20in%20new%20Azerbaijan%20border%20flare-up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707828511000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0FB7%2Fproduction%2F_132632040_gettyimages-1693027774.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68283041%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20attack%20is%20the%20deadliest%20since%20Armenia%20and%20Azerbaijan%20began%20discussing%20a%20peace%20deal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68283041%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68283041.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68283041.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tom%20Cruise%20Make