A%20food%2C%20housing%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20water%20among%20others%20and%2C%20lastly%2C%20that%20there%20has%20been%20no%20major%20communal%20violence%20since%202014%20and%20that%20India%20has%20been%20most%20peaceful%20during%20the%20last%2050%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20appeals%20are%20based%20on%20half%20truths%20and%20ignore%20the%20core%20problem%20which%20shapes%20the%20lives%20of%20Muslims%20in%20India.%20True%2C%20some%20elite%20Muslims%20may%20not%20be%20facing%20the%20problems%20so%20severely%20but%20overall%20the%20central%20issue%20of%20insecurity%2C%20marginalisation%20and%20ghettoisation%20as%20a%20whole%20is%20not%20accounted%20for%20in%20such%20appeals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20point%20that%20there%20is%20no%20major%20violence%20against%20Muslims%20since%202014%20is%20a%20blatant%20lie.%20The%20horrific%20Delhi%20violence%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20massive%20Shaheen%20Bagh%20movement%2C%20instigated%20by%20BJP%20worthies%20%E2%80%93%20who%20can%20forget%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwatch-bjp-kapil-mishra-interview-delhi-riots%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Egoli%20maaro%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20threats%20of%20forcible%20removal%20of%20protesters%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%2051%20people%2C%2037%20of%20those%20being%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F17171339%2FScreen-Shot-2020-03-17-at-5.13.15-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221049%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F17171339%2FScreen-Shot-2020-03-17-at-5.13.15-PM.png%201049w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F17171339%2FScreen-Shot-2020-03-17-at-5.13.15-PM-300x183.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewir