%20their%20right%20to%20protest%20and%20the%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20the%20people%20by%20their%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20march%2C%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20has%20called%20for%20an%20amicable%20settlement%20by%20all%20parties%20and%20said%20that%20law%20and%20order%20should%20be%20maintained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20sought%20a%20status%20report%20on%20the%20protest%20--%20which%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FVideo%3A%2520Protesting%2520Farmers%2520Throw%2520Barriers%2520From%2520Flyover%2C%2520Face%2520Water%2520Cannons%5C%22%3Eresulted%20in%20chaos%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20borders%20between%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Haryana%20and%20a%20traffic%20mess%20on%20the%20Delhi-UP%20border%20--%C2%A0%20from%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20governments%20of%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana.%20It%20has%20also%20made%20the%20Delhi%20government%20a%20party%20to%20the%20petitions%20and%20will%20hear%20its%20side%20during%20the%20next%20hearing%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Tuesday's%20hearing%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Acting%20Chief%20Justice%20GS%20Sandhawalia%20and%20Justice%20Lapita%20Banerji%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20has%20to%20be%20balance%20in%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20speech%20and%20expression%2C%20no%20right%20exists%20in%20isolation.%20The%20issue%20should%20be%20resolved%20amicably%20between%20all%20parties%20and%20areas%20should%20be%20identified%20by%20the%20states%20where%20the%20protest%20can%20be%20held...%20Use%20of%20force%20should%20be%20the%20last%20resort.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20observations%20came%20amid%20reports%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-updates-farmers-set-to-march-towards-delhi-borders-sealed-5047690%5C%22%3Edrones%20being%20used%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20drop%20tear%20gas%20on%20the%20farmers%20and%20the%20protestors%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftear-gas-fired-at-farmers-marching-towards-delhi-at-punjab-haryana-border-5048511%5C%22%3Ethrowing%20stones%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Right%20To%20Free%20Movement'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20PILs%20have%20been%20filed%20in%20the%20court%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20march.%20The%20first%20petition%20argued%20that%2C%20India%20being%20a%20democratic%20republic%2C%20preventing%20farmers%20from%20reaching%20Delhi%20and%20protesting%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20their%20right%20to%20free%20movement%2C%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20right%20to%20peaceful%20protest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20sought%20the%20lifting%20of%20internet%20suspension%20in%20seven%20districts%20of%20Haryana%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20prohibitory%20orders%20under%20Section%20144%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Procedure%20Code%20have%20been%20imposed%20in%2015%20districts%20of%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20reports%20of%20barbed%20wires%20being%20put%20up%20and%20nails%20being%20laid%20down%20on%20some%20roads%2C%20the%20petitioner%20said%20fundamental%20rights%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution%20have%20been%20violated%20with%20the%20government%20stopping%20the%20farmers%20at%20various%20borders.%20The%20petition%20also%20highlighted%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20upheld%20the%20right%20to%20protest%20and%20assist%20in%20peaceful%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Cannot%20Cause%20Inconvenience'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20PIL%2C%20filed%20by%20a%20lawyer%2C%20Arvind%20Seth%2C%20argued%20that%20thousands%20of%20vehicles%20are%20moving%20towards%20Delhi%20and%20said%20that%20no%20one%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20block%20national%20highways.%20The%20petition%20claimed%20that%20people%20are%20facing%20inconvenience%20and%20even%20those%20going%20to%20hospitals%20are%20having%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(the%20farmers)%20can%20oppose%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20government%20but%20they%20cannot%20do%20so%20anywhere%20they%20choose%20and%20cause%20inconvenience%20to%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petition%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernments'%20Stand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20representing%20the%20Centre%20said%20the%20government%20is%20ready%20for%20negotiations%20with%20the%20farmers%2C%20including%20on%20their%20key%20issue%20of%20a%20law%20on%20minimum%20support%20price.%20The%20lawyer%20pointed%20out%20that%20a%20committee%20on%20MSP%20had%20been%20formed%20in%202022%20and%20the%20farmers%20had%20not%20sent%20their%20representatives.%20%26quot%3BMeetings%20can%20be%20held%20with%20the%20protesting%20farmers'%20representatives%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActing%20Chief%20Justice%20Sandhawalia%20then%20asked%20the%20Haryana%20government%20why%20it%20had%20blocked%20the%20borders%20when%20the%20farmers%20were%20passing%20through%20the%20state%2C%20and%20observed%20that%20they%20have%20the%20right%20to%20come%20and%20go.%20The%20state%20responded%20that%20it%20had%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20since%20there%20was%20a%20call%20to%20gather%205%20km%20before%20the%20Delhi%20border%20and%20claimed%20that%20the%20farmers'%20tractors%20have%20been%20modified%20to%20include%20weaponry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20pointed%20out%20that%20Section%20144%20has%20been%20in%20force%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20since%20the%20last%20farmers'%20protest%2C%20where%20there%20had%20been%20some%20%26quot%3Bcriminal%20incidents%26quot%3B%20in%20Haryana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Punjab%20government%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20said%20there%20was%20merit%20in%20the%20farmers'%20demands%20and%20that%20it%20would%20allow%20peaceful%20protests.%20It%20said%20adequate%20arrangements%20have%20been%20made%20for%20crowd%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20all%20sides%2C%20the%20court%20said%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20have%20rights%20but%20the%20State%20also%20has%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20protect%20people%20on%20the%20roads%2C%20who%20have%20rights%20too.%20It%20said%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20should%20ensure%20that%20the%20protest%20is%20held%20only%20in%20designated%20places%20and%20urged%20all%20parties%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%20amicably%20before%20adjourning%20the%20matter%20till%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707826500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fgomrbat_punjab-farmers-delhi-protest_625x300_13_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fresolve-issue-amicably-punjab-and-haryana-high-court-on-farmer-protests-5050345%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hearing%20two%20differing%20petitions%20on%20farmers%20not%20being%20able%20to%20exercise%20their%20right%20to%20protest%20and%20the%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20the%20people%20by%20their%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20march%2C%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20has%20called%20for%20an%20amicable%20settlement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fresolve-issue-amicably-punjab-and-haryana-high-court-on-farmer-protests-5050345%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fresolve-issue-amicably-punjab-and-haryana-high-court-on-farmer-protests-5050345%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fresolve-issue-amicably-punjab-and-haryana-high-court-on-farmer-protests-5050345%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Will%20Dance%20In%20Wheelchair%26quot%3B%3A%20Woman%20At%20PM%20Modi%20Event%20In%20Abu%20Dhabi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20in%20a%20wheelchair%20but%20says%20that%20she%20doesn't%20care%20and%20intends%20to%20enjoy%20herself.%20The%20elderly%20woman%20has%20travelled%20from%20Dubai%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20'Ahlan%20Modi'%20(Hello%2C%20Modi)%20event%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20received%20a%20rousing%20welcome%20as%20he%20arrived%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20today.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20welcomed%20by%20UAE%20President%20Mohammed%20bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan.%20The%20two%20leaders%20shook%20hands%20and%20hugged%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20motivation%20is%20love%20for%20my%20country%20because%20I%20love%20Bharat.%20From%2048%20years%20I%20am%20here%20then%20also%20dil%20is%20Hindustani.%20So%20knee%20surgery%20and%20all%20is%20khali%20vali%20(not%20important)%20and%20I%20don't%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20in%20wheelchair%20told%20NDTV%20when%20asked%20about%20her%20motivation.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BFrom%20two%20days%20I%20was%20thinking%20what%20to%20wear...%20See%20my%20nails%2C%20my%20rings%2C%20my%20bindi%2C%20my%20scarf%2C%20everything%2C%20total%20Hindustani%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%20underscoring%20her%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20is%20set%20to%20address%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20at%20%26quot%3BAhlan%20Modi%26quot%3B%20event.%20Organised%20by%20the%20Indian%20community%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20the%20event%20has%20gathered%20unprecedented%20attention%2C%20with%20over%2065%2C000%20registrations%2C%20reflecting%20the%20overwhelming%20response%20from%20the%20Indian%20expatriate%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20enjoy.%20I%20will%20dance%20in%20wheelchair%2C%20no%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20told%20NDTV%2C%20flashing%20a%20big%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20expatriate%20community%20of%20approximately%203.5%20million%20is%20the%20largest%20ethnic%20community%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20constituting%20roughly%2035%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20country's%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20of%20the%20Indian%20People%20Forum%20and%20leader%20of%20the%20'Ahlan%20Modi'%20initiative%2C%20Jitendra%20Vaidya%2C%20expressed%20his%20happiness%20and%20anticipation%20for%20the%20ground-breaking%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20gates%20are%20yet%20to%20open%2C%20but%20people%20are%20already%20standing%20at%20each%20gate%20of%20this%20stadium.%20I%20can%20say%20this%20with%20guarantee%20that%20whenever%20people%20will%20remember%20a%20public%20event%20of%20PM%20Modi%20outside%20the%20country%2C%20'Ahlan%20Modi'%20will%20be%20remembered%20as%20a%20landmark%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707826080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fs4ame9m8_woman-wheelchair-1200_625x300_13_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-will-dance-in-wheelchair-woman-at-pm-modi-event-in-abu-dhabi-5050355%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20is%20in%20a%20wheelchair%20but%20says%20that%20she%20doesn't%20care%20and%20intends%20to%20enjoy%20herself.%20The%20elderly%20woman%20has%20travelled%20from%20Dubai%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20Ahlan%20Modi%20(Hello%2C%20Modi)%20event%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-will-dance-in-wheelchair-woman-at-pm-modi-event-in-abu-dhabi-5050355%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-will-dance-in-wheelchair-woman-at-pm-modi-event-in-abu-dhabi-5050355%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-will-dance-in-wheelchair-woman-at-pm-modi-event-in-abu-dhabi-5050355%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20Is%20All%20But%20Certain%20To%20Make%20His%20Debut%20In%20Rajkot%20Test%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20months%20of%20wait%20is%20set%20to%20end%20for%20uncapped%20India%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sarfaraz%20Khan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64385-sarfaraz-naushad-khan-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESarfaraz%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20all%20but%20set%20to%20make%20his%