C%20and%20the%20reason%20why%20I%20know%20is%20because%20I%20was%20coming%20to%20my%20room%20when%20they%20were%20taking%20the%20body%20out.%26quot%3B%20The%20content%20creator%20said%20it%20was%20something%20%26quot%3Bvery%2C%20very%20sad%26quot%3B%20to%20have%20witnessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'I'm%20thinking%20it%20was%20probably%20a%20heart%20attack.%20But%20I%20don't%20have%20much%20news%20other%20than%20it%20was%20a%20female%20elderly%20patient%2C%20or%20guest%2C%20that%20passed%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20Adita%20stated%20in%20her%20response%20to%20a%20comment%20that%20the%20woman%20%C2%A0%26quot%3Bwas%20a%20solo%20guest%2C%20so%20she%20passed%20alone%20in%20her%20room.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20outlet%2C%20the%20cruise%20line%20operator%20revealed%20that%20one%20of%20its%20passengers%20had%20passed%20away%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20discuss%20the%20circumstances%20surrounding%20the%20death.%20%26quot%3BA%20guest%20sailing%20onboard%20Serenade%20of%20the%20Seas%20has%20sadly%20passed%20away.%20We%20are%20actively%20providing%20support%20and%20assistance%20to%20the%20guest's%20loved%20ones%20at%20this%20time.%20Out%20of%20the%20privacy%20of%20the%20guest%20and%20their%20family%2C%20we%20have%20nothing%20further%20to%20share%20at%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F02%2F12%2Fworld-news%2Froyal-caribbean-passenger-dies-aboard-9-month-world-cruise-report%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20many%20large%20cruise%20ships%20have%20both%20morgues%20and%20body%20bags%20in%20case%20there%20is%20an%20untimely%20death%20while%20out%20at%20sea.%20Depending%20on%20what%20arrangements%20can%20be%20made%20for%20the%20transportation%20of%20the%20remains%2C%20the%20bodies%20of%20persons%20who%20pass%20away%20while%20at%20sea%20are%20normally%20stored%20in%20the%20mortuary%20until%20th