%20a%20day%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-updates-farmers-set-to-march-towards-delhi-borders-sealed-5047690%5C%22%3Efarmers%20began%20their%20'Delhi%20%3Cem%3EChalo%3C%2Fem%3E'%20march%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20push%20for%20their%20demands%2C%20including%20legislation%20guaranteeing%20a%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20for%20crops%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20has%20told%20NDTV%20that%20such%20a%20law%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Dr%20RB%20Singh%2C%20a%20Padma%20Bhushan%20awardee%20and%20member%20of%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20farmers%20to%20get%20the%20right%20price%20for%20their%20crops%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20make%20a%20new%20law%20on%20MSP%20in%20the%20country%20to%20properly%20implement%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20commission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Singh%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20panel%20had%20recommended%20that%20MSP%20should%20be%20fixed%20at%20a%20level%20which%20is%20at%20least%2050%25%20higher%20than%20the%20cost%20of%20production%20of%20any%20crop.%20%26quot%3BBut%20this%20system%20has%20not%20been%20implemented%20in%20a%20uniform%20manner%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%201%20lakh%20farmers%2C%20who%20have%20the%20support%20of%20about%20200%20farmer%20unions%2C%20began%20marching%20towards%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday.%20Among%20the%20key%20demands%20of%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20are%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20for%20MSP%20-%C2%A0%20which%20will%20shield%20them%20from%20the%20vagaries%20of%20the%20market%20-%20loan%20waivers%2C%20and%20implementation%20of%20other%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20recommendations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20was%20set%20up%20in%202004%20and%20submitted%20five%20reports%2C%20with%20the%20last%20one%20in%20October%202006.%20Last%20week%2C%20the%20govern