he%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20has%20told%20NDTV%20that%20such%20a%20law%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-farmers-protest-swaminathan-commission-member-backs-law-on-msp-5049932%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-farmers-protest-swaminathan-commission-member-backs-law-on-msp-5049932%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-farmers-protest-swaminathan-commission-member-backs-law-on-msp-5049932%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Refuses%20To%20Stay%20Law%20To%20Appoint%20Election%20Commissioners%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupreme-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20refused%2C%20for%20a%20second%20time%2C%20to%20ban%20a%20contentious%20new%20law%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Felection-commission-bill%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappointment%20of%20election%20commissioners%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20court%20has%2C%20though%2C%20added%20the%20petition%20to%20a%20list%20of%20pending%20cases%20on%20this%20subject%20and%20directed%20that%20all%20these%20be%20heard%20in%20April%2C%20potentially%20days%20before%20a%20general%20election.%20The%20court%20has%20also%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20central%20government%20seeking%20a%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20petition%20has%20been%20filed%20by%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%20an%20apolitical%20and%20non-partisan%20non-profit%20organisation%20working%20electoral%20and%20political%20reforms%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hearing%20today%2C%20Advocate%20on%20Record%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20arguing%20for%20ADR%2C%20said%20the%20law%20had%20to%20be%20banned%20now%20since%20one%20of%20the%20election%20commissioners%2C%20Anup%20Chandra%20Pandey%2C%20is%20to%20retire%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20operative%20section%20of%20the%20new%20law%20-%20which%20states%20appointments%20are%20based%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20a%20three-member%20committee%20led%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20including%20a%20member%20of%20the%20union%20cabinet%2C%20and%20not%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20-%20remains%2C%20Mr%20Bhushan%20said%2C%20the%20petition%20becomes%20%26quot%3Bineffective%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbill-to-appoint-top-3-election-commissioners-passed-in-lok-sabha-4715210%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBill%20To%20Appoint%20Top%203%20Poll%20Officers%20Passed%20In%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Clears%20Parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20two-member%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjeev%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Gupta%20disagreed%20and%20said%20matters%20of%20%26quot%3Bconstitutional%20validity%20are%20never%20infructuous%20(unnecessary)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSorry%2C%20we%20cannot%20grant%20you%20interim%20relief.%20Matter%20of%20constitutional%20validity%20never%20becomes%20infructuous.%20We%20know%20our%20parameters%20for%20granting%20interim%20relief%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20told%20Mr%20Bhushan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20too%2C%20the%20court%20refused%20to%20ban%20the%20law%20-%20on%20a%20petition%20by%20the%20Congress'%20Jaya%20Thakur%20-%20but%20said%20it%20was%20ready%20to%20'test'%20it%2C%20and%20issued%20notices%20to%20the%20centre%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Thakur's%20petition%20also%20demanded%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20law%2C%20which%20critics%20say%20gives%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20ruling%20BJP%20an%20iron%20grip%20over%20naming%20Election%20Commissioners%2C%20and%20thereby%20control%20over%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20which%20regulates%20and%20oversees%20all%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20have%20called%20for%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20to%20be%20included%2C%20to%20balance%20out%20any%20potential%20conflict%20of%20interests%20that%20might%20be%20raised%20by%20the%20presence%20of%20politicians%20on%20the%20appointment%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-stay-new-law-on-appointment-of-chief-election-commissioner-election-commissioners-issues-notice-to-centre-4847493%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20Won't%20Stay%20New%20Law%20On%20Naming%20Election%20Commissioners%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20in%20March%20last%20year%20the%20court%20did%20say%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20would%20be%20the%20third%20member%20of%20the%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that%20ruling%20was%20controversially%20overturned%3B%20the%20government%20passed%20a%20bill%20replacing%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20with%20a%20member%20of%20the%20union%20cabinet%20to%20be%20nominated%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20December%20even%20as%20most%20of%20the%20opposition%20was%20suspended.%20The%20opposition%20attacked%20the%20proposed%20law%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20compromise%20the%20poll%20panel's%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707822300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fcq5c2cmg_supreme-court-reuters_625x300_06_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%