0leadership%20of%20the%20party.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20party%20knows%20how%20to%20utilise%20the%20senior%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20son%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Shankarrao%20Chavan%2C%20Ashok%20Chavan%20wields%20significant%20influence%20in%20Nanded%20region.%20His%20exit%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20--%20comprising%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20camp%20of%20NCP%20and%20the%20Congress%20--%20faces%20two%20tall%20poll%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chavan%20has%20held%20key%20roles%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20including%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20chief%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee.%20He%20has%20served%20as%20an%20MP%20from%20Nanded%20on%20two%20occasions%20and%20been%20a%20member%20of%20both%20Houses%20of%20the%20state%20legislature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20serving%20as%20state%20minister%2C%20he%20was%20chosen%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20after%20Vilasrao%20Deshmukh%20stepped%20down%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202008%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%20Congress%20retained%20him%20on%20the%20top%20post%20after%20the%202009%20state%20polls.%20The%20stint%20was%2C%20however%2C%20short%20as%20Mr%20Chavan%20was%20forced%20to%20step%20down%20amid%20corruption%20allegations%20related%20to%20the%20Adarsh%20Housing%20Society%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20corruption%20allegations%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20court%20has%20ruled%20in%20our%20favour.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chavan%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20quit%20the%20Congress%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20one.%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20take%20this%20decision%20in%20a%20day.%20I%20have%20taken%20this%20decision%20for%20the%20people%20of%20my%20district.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20the%20Congress%20gave%20me%20a%20lot.%20But%20I%20have%20also%20served%20it%20well%2C%26quot%