%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20rounds%20of%20talks%20with%20farmers%20were%20inconclusive.%20Further%20discussion%20is%20necessary%20to%20reach%20a%20solution%20and%20we%20ready%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Arjun%20Munda%2C%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Agriculture%20and%20Farmers'%20Welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20must%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20others%20don't%20try%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20their%20protest%2C%20he%20said%2C%20urging%20them%20to%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-months-ration-diesel-in-trollies-punjab-farmers-ready-for-long-haul-5048346%5C%22%3E%26quot%3B6%20Months'%20Ration%2C%20Diesel%20In%20Trollies%26quot%3B%3A%20Punjab%20Farmers%20Ready%20For%20Long%20Haul%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20forces%20among%20them%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20defame%20the%20farmers.%20Avoid%20such%20people.%20The%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20farmers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Munda%20was%20in%20the%20government%20delegation%20that%20met%20the%20farmer%20leaders%20yesterday%20in%20Chandigarh%20to%20convince%20them%20to%20call%20off%20their%20march%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20meeting%20led%20to%20an%20agreement%20over%20a%20few%20demands%2C%20no%20consensus%20could%20be%20reached%20on%20three%20key%20ones%2C%20including%20the%20enactment%20of%20a%20law%20guaranteeing%20a%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP).%20%26quot%3BOn%20some%20issues%2C%20we%20will%20need%20to%20consult%20the%20states.%20We%20will%20find%20a%20way%20out.%20We%20are%20always%20ready%20to%20talk%20and%20find%20a%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%20following%20the%20talks%20late%20last%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-ne