ploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13143422%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-2.33.41.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20prime%20time%20Fox%20News%20host%20Tucker%20Carlson%20%E2%80%93%20long%20known%20as%20a%20public%20cheerleader%20for%20Donald%20Trump%20%E2%80%93%20has%20conducted%20a%20wide-ranging%20two-hour%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhat-has-former-fox-news-host-tucker-carlson-said-on-putin-the-war-and-ukraine-13066018%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Russian%20president%2C%20Vladimir%20Putin.%20Carlson%2C%20who%20has%20consistently%20argued%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20case%20for%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20posted%20his%20interview%20on%20both%20his%20own%20site%20and%20on%20Elon%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%20There%20%E2%80%93%20according%20to%20Kremlin%20mouthpiece%20Pravda%20%E2%80%93%20it%20chalked%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpravda-en.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2F02%2F09%2F311590.html%5C%22%3Emore%20than%2090%20million%20views%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20hours%20of%20being%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20pair%20faced%20each%20other%20in%20a%20large%2C%20virtually%20empty%20Kremlin%20office%2C%20Putin%20immediately%20put%20Carlson%20on%20the%20defensive%2C%20demanding%3A%20%E2%80%9CAre%20we%20having%20a%20talk%20show%20or%20serious%20conversation%3F%E2%80%9D%20He%20then%20gave%20his%20interlocutor%20a%2025-minute%20history%20lesson%20%E2%80%93%20a%20mix%20of%20mythical%20and%20actual%20history%20going%20back%20over%20a%20millennium%20%E2%80%93%20to%20show%20both%20how%20Ukrainians%20and%20Russians%20were%20not%20really%20separate%20peoples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20took%20pains%20to%20assert%20from%20the%20start%20who%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftuckercarlson.com%2Fthe-vladimir-putin-interview%2F%5C%22%3Erunning%20the%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20early%20on.%20It%20was%20a%20classic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2007%2F06%2F14%2Fputin-uses-dog-to-intimidate-merkel%2F%5C%22%3EPutin%20powerplay%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20that%2C%20it%20was%20plain%20sailing%20for%20Putin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interview%20was%20wide-ranging%3A%20Ukraine%2C%20China%2C%20multi-polarity%2C%20Putin%E2%80%99s%20opinion%20of%20several%20former%20US%20presidents%20as%20well%20as%20his%20predecessors%20Lenin%2C%20Stalin%20and%20Yeltsin.%20Discussing%20US%20politics%2C%20Putin%20touched%20on%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20what%20he%20called%20the%20warlike%20%E2%80%9Cmindsets%E2%80%9D%20of%20US%20foreign%20policy%20elites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FhYfByTcY49k%3Fsi%3DcWnlyonxtuBf6lv_%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENato%20slammed%2C%20Maga%20boosted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20predictably%20the%20Russia%20president%20blamed%20what%20he%20identified%20as%20Nato%20expansionism%20and%20threats%20to%20his%20country%E2%80%99s%20security.%20He%20recounted%20how%20he%20had%20offered%20a%20hand%20of%20friendship%20to%20the%20US%3A%20%E2%80%9CPlease%20don%E2%80%99t%20%5Bexpand%20Nato%20eastward%5D.%20We%20are%20as%20bourgeois%20now%20as%20you%20are.%20We%20are%20a%20market%20economy%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20Communist%20party%20power.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20negotiate.%E2%80%9D%20But%20his%20overtures%20were%20spurned%20by%20the%20US%20elites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20predictably%2C%20both%20interviewer%20and%20interviewee%20took%20the%20opportunity%20to%20boost%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20Make%20America%20Great%20Again%20(Maga)%20voter%20base.%20Trump%20has%20already%20said%20he%20would%20end%20US%20military%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20quickly%E2%80%9D%20by%20withdrawing%20US%20aid%2C