sial%20interview%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2023%2F34%2Fspecial-articles%2Fpoly-crisis-or-organic-crisis.html%5C%22%3Egreat%20turmoil%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20the%20US%20and%20internationally.%20Trump%20%E2%80%93%20for%20whom%20Carlson%20campaigned%20in%20the%202020%20election%20campaign%20%E2%80%93%20faces%20a%20string%20of%20court%20cases%2C%20including%20some%20that%20could%20%E2%80%93%20if%20he%E2%80%99s%20convicted%20%E2%80%93%20see%20him%20imprisoned%20before%20the%20November%202024%20presidential%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2024%2Ffeb%2F07%2Fus-supreme-court-trump-case-eligible-for-2024-run%5C%22%3Ealso%20rule%20on%3C%2Fa%3E%20whether%20Trump%20should%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20ballot%20altogether%20due%20to%20charges%20of%20insurrectionary%20conduct%20on%20January%206%202021.%20Congress%20also%20remains%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2023%2Fdec%2F07%2Fbiden-ukraine-funding-bill-mexico-border%5C%22%3Eat%20loggerheads%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20providing%20further%20financial%20support%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20win%20the%20Republican%20presidential%20nomination%2C%20Trump%20faces%20a%20primary%20challenge%20from%20Nikki%20Haley%2C%20who%20now%20represents%20an%20important%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1080%2F14747731.2021.1991660%5C%22%3Efocal%20point%20of%20opposition%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Trump%20the%20personality%20rather%20than%20to%20Trumpism%20the%20idea.%20Haley%2C%20former%20governor%20of%20South%20Carolina%20and%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20ambassador%20to%20the%20UN%2C%20is%20also%20a%20champion%20of%20US%20support%20for%20Ukraine%E2%80%99s%20resistance%20to%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20military%20might%20%E2%80%93%20as%20is%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20hr