20an%20extension%20of%20the%20ideological%20sentiments%20conveyed%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Esarkha%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20slogan%20also%20reflects%20the%20complexity%20of%20Yemeni%20views%20about%20US%20counterterrorism%20interventions%20and%20the%20widespread%20belief%20that%20these%20have%20provided%20terrorist%20groups%20with%20the%20oxygen%20they%20need%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreignaffairs.com%2Farticles%2Fyemen%2F2015-08-30%2Fassisting-al-qaeda%5C%22%3Esurvive%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerror%20groups%20as%20a%20tool%20of%20the%20state%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20long%20been%20criticised%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheintercept.com%2Fdrone-papers%2F%5C%22%3Edisproportionately%3C%2Fa%3E%20killing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2012%2F06%2F14%2Fopinion%2Fhow-drones-help-al-qaeda.html%5C%22%3Ecivilians%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20counterterrorism%20strikes.%20Some%20experts%20argue%20this%20may%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1111%2Fj.1475-4967.2011.00502.x%5C%22%3Ecreate%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20%E2%80%9Cterrorists%E2%80%9D%20than%20it%20kills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20critique%3A%20it%20was%20the%20Central%20Intelligence%20Agency%20(CIA)%20that%20originally%20supported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F29768089%3Fseq%3D2%5C%22%3EOsama%20bin%20Laden%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20mujahideen%20in%20Afghanistan%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20trap%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20in%20an%20unwinnable%20war%2C%20making%20the%20US%20at%20least%20somewhat%20responsible%20for%20what%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20other%20layers%20to%20these%20slogans%20that%20are%20less%20intuitively%20understood%20by%20a%20Western%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%E2%80%99s%20reflexive%20support%20for%20authoritarian%20leaders%20who%20claim%20to%20be%20targeting%20terrorism%20is%20widely%20seen%20in%20Yemen%20(and%20throughout%20the%20Middle%20East)%20as%20fuelling%20a%20symbiotic%20relationship%20between%20oppressive%20regimes%2C%20terrorist%20groups%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hurstpublishers.com%2Fbook%2Fthe-middle-east-crisis-factory%2F%5C%22%3EWestern-led%20military%20interventions%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20in%20the%20region%2C%20groups%20like%20al-Qaeda%20and%20Islamic%20State%20function%2C%20in%20part%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Ctools%E2%80%9D%20that%20Western-backed%20authoritarian%20leaders%20use%20to%20maintain%20their%20power.%20They%20provide%20plausible%20deniability%20for%20the%20violence%20these%20leaders%20use%20against%20civilians%2C%20or%20support%20their%20pitch%20that%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1080%2F09636412.2023.2250253%5C%22%3Eif%20I%E2%80%99m%20gone%2C%20terrorists%20will%20take%20over%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Yemen%2C%20there%20is%20a%20long%20history%20of%20allegations%20that%20Western-backed%20leaders%20have%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.middleeasteye.net%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-yemenis-are-still-joining-al-qaeda%5C%22%3Ereleased%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Ftunnel-rats-terror-113197%5C%22%3Eal-Qaeda%20prisoners%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20they%20could%20regroup%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2015%2F6%2F4%2Finformant-says-yemens-saleh-helped-direct-al-qaeda%5C%22%3Efacilitated%3C%2Fa%3E%20al-Qaeda%20attacks%20against%20local%20and%20foreign%20targets%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Emisdirected%20US%20strikes%20to%20kill%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fonline.wsj.com%2Farticle%2FSB10001424052970203899504577126883574284126.html%5C%22%3Epolitical%20opponents%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20al-Qaeda%20leaders.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%E2%80%99s%20regional%20partners%2C%20such%20as%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20have%20also%20been%20accused%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.middleeasteye.net%2Fnews%2Fuae-recruited-alqaeda-assassinations-yemen-report%5C%22%3Erecruiting%3C%2Fa%3E%20al-Qaeda%20members%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fctc.westpoint.edu%2Ftwenty-years-after-9-11-the-jihadi-threat-in-the-arabian-peninsula%2F%5C%22%3Efight%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67945137%5C%22%3Eparamilitary%3C%2Fa%3E%20forces%20against%20Yemeni%20opponents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20many%20Yemenis%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20view%20al-Qaeda%20or%20Islamic%20State%20as%20being%20completely%20separate%20from%20those%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20country.%20Rather%2C%20they%20often%20see%20these%20terrorist%20groups%20as%20helping%20to%20reinforce%20the%20status%20quo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20view%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20diametrically%20opposed%20to%20Western%20understandings%20of%20al-Qaeda%20or%20Islamic%20State.%20In%20the%20West%2C%20these%20groups%20are%20framed%20as%20rebels%20seeking%20to%20overturn%20the%20state.%20But%20across%20the%20region%2C%20many%20believe%20these%20relationships%20defy%20simple%20categories%20like%20%E2%80%9Cstate%20versus%20insurgent%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cfriend%20versus%20enemy%E2%80%9D%20because%20terror%20groups%20can%20be%20both%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20Yemeni%20analyst%20articulated%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1080%2F09636412.2023.2250253%5C%22%3Efrustration%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20trying%20to%20explain%20the%20symbiotic%20relationship%20between%20terrorist%20groups%20and%20authoritarian%20leaders%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20easier%20to%20tell%20a%20kid%20that%20Santa%20Claus%20isn%E2%80%99t%20real%20than%20to%20get%20foreigners%20to%20see%20what%20al-Qaeda%20in%20Yemen%20really%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20the%20West%E2%80%99s%20policies%20are%20backfiring%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Houthis%2C%20America%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20role%20in%20helping%20to%20fuel%20terrorist%20groups%20has%20been%20a%20longstanding%20part%20of%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20messaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20decade%20ago%20%E2%80%93%20two%20years%20before%20the%20Houthis%20seized%20the%20Yemeni%20capital%20and%20sparked%20a%20lengthy%20war%20%E2%80%93%20I%20visited%20a%20northern%20town%20where%20there%20were%20several%20large%2C%20freshly%20painted%20murals%20bearing%20the%20statement%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1177%2F1354066119837335%5C%22%3Eal-Qaeda%20is%20American%20made%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20residents%20about%20the%20this%2C%20they%20appeared%20to%20see%20the%20statement%20as%20a%20banal%20declaration%20of%20fact.%20They%20were%20more%20impressed%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnice%20handwriting%E2%80%9D%20than%20the%20message.%20(Like%20the%20banners%20bearing%20the%20%3Cem%3Esarkha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20murals%20used%20a%20red%20barbed-wire%20font%20for%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9CAmerica%E2%80%9D.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis%E2%80%99%20message%20about%20American%20complicity%20in%20terrorism%20resonates%20because%20it%20works%20at%20several%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20gestures%20to%20the%20violence%20unleashed%20by%20the%20US-led%20invasion%20and%20occupation%20of%20Iraq%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F25%2Fas-us-resists-ceasefire-calls-what-is-bidens-endgame-in-gaza%5C%22%3Enear-unconditional%3C%2Fa%3E%20support%20the%20US%20provides%20to%20Israel%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2011%2Fapr%2F05%2Fbritain-let-weapons-be-used-for-repression%5C%22%3Emilitary%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjacobin.com%2F2020%2F03%2Fegypt-prison-state-client-mubarak-al-sisi%5C%22%3Ecarceral%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rand.org%2Fpubs%2Fcommentary%2F2013%2F07%2Fhalting-aid-to-egypt-over-military-coup-would-hurt.html%5C%22%3Epolitical%3C%2Fa%3E%20support%20the%20US%20and%20its%20Western%20partners%20provide%20authoritarian%20leaders%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20gets%20at%20the%20profound%20sense%20within%20Yemen%20(and%20across%20the%20region)%20that%20the%20political%20status%20quo%20is%20sustained%20by%20violent%20regimes.%20And%20that%20terrorist%20groups%20like%20al-Qaeda%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20counterterrorism%20interventions%20they%20invite%20%E2%80%93%20are%20part%20of%20how%20those%20regimes%20maintain%20their%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20violence%20the%20Houthis%20use%20to%20sustain%20their%20own%20power%20is%20an%20irony%20that%20should%20not%20be%20lost.%20The%20Houthis%20are%20widely%20despised%20by%20Yemenis%20who%20live%20under%20their%20rule.%20Even%20so%2C%20their%20messaging%20taps%20into%20widespread%20views%20about%20the%20drivers%20of%20regional%20violence%20that%20some%20Western%20observers%20have%20long%20dismissed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20the%20complexities%20that%20underpin%20the%20Houthis%E2%80%99%20new%20slogan%20help%20explain%20why%20Western%20policy%20across%20the%20region%20will%20continue%20to%20backfire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPut%20bluntly%2C%20people%20in%20the%20region%20see%20Western%20policymakers%20as%20blind%20to%20their%20historical%20record%20of%20strengthening%20the%20enemies%20they%20come%20to%20fight.%20The%20fact%20that%20Western%20airstrikes%20are%20giving%20the%20Houthis%20a%20legitimacy%20that%20was%20previously%20unimaginable%20is%20ominous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%20for%20Yemeni%20civilians%2C%20the%20Houthis%E2%80%99%20stance%20against%20Israel%20will%20increase%20their%20appeal%20to%20those%20who%20know%20little%20of%20what%20it%20is%20like%20to%20live%20with%20them.%20It%20will%20also%20make%20it%20even%20harder%20for%20Yemenis%20to%20dislodge%20them%20from%20power.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F222865%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Fsarah-g-phillips-1504022%5C%22%3ESarah%20G.%20Phillips%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Non-Resident%20Fellow%20at%20the%20Sana%E2%80%99a%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20Studies%2C%20Yemen%3B%20Professor%20of%20Global%20Conflict%20and%20Development%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Funiversity-of-sydney-841%5C%22%3EUniversity%20of%20Sydney%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Famerica-is-the-mother-of-terrorism-why-the-houthis-new-slogan-is-important-for-understanding-the-middle-east-222865%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707814806000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F24190536%2Fimage-1788.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Famerica-is-the-mother-of-terrorism-why-the-houthis-new-slogan-matters%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20slogan%20reflects%20the%20complexity%20of%20Yemeni%20views%20about%20US%20counterterrorism%20interventions%20and%20the%20widespread%20belief%20that%20these%20have%20provided%20terrorist%20groups%20with%20the%20oxygen%20they%20need%20to%20survive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Famerica-is-the-mother-of-terrorism-why-the-houthis-new-slogan-matters%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Police%20Use%20Tear%20Gas%20on%20Protesting%20Farmers%20at%20Punjab-Haryana%20Border%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13142417%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-2.14.07-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalandhar%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EChaos%20prevailed%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20Shambu%20border%20on%20Tuesday%20(February%2013)%20afternoon%2C%20after%20the%20Haryana%20police%20fired%20tear%20gas%20at%20protesting%20farmers.%20The%20farmers%20are%20trying%20to%20reach%20the%20national%20capital%20for%20their%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest%2C%20and%20were%20breaking%20and%20removing%20barricades%20at%20the%20border%20when%20the%20police%20fired%20tear%20gas%20at%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20of%20farmers%20being%20detained%20by%20the%20Haryana%20police%20were%20also%20doing%20the%20rounds%20in%20the%20chaos.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20official%20confirmation%20either%20from%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unions%20or%20the%20Haryana%20police%20about%20this%20yet.%20Farmers%20on%20a%20long%20cavalcade%20of%20over%203%2C000%20tractor%20trailers%20were%20seen%20running%20helter-skelter%20to%20save%20themselves%20at%20the%20Shambu%20border%2C%20on%20the%20Punjab%20side.%20The%20Haryana%20police%20has%20also%20deployed%20drones%20to%20keep%20a%20watch%20and%20record%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20could%20be%20seen%20covering%20their%20faces%20with%20clothes%20and%20masks%20to%20save%20themselves%20from%20the%20tear%20gas.%20The%20farmers%20a%20waiting%20for%20union%20leaders%20to%20reach%20the%20Shambu%20border%2C%20after%20which%20they%20will%20cross%20over%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20shared%20by%20farmers%2C%20many%20could%20be%20seen%20finding%20it%20hard%20to%20breathe.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20finding%20it%20hard%20to%20breathe%20and%20have%20stopped%20for%20a%20while.%20For%20the%20time%20being%2C%20we%20have%20been%20asked%20by%20the%20farmer%20union%20leaders%20to%20stop%20till%20they%20give%20us%20the%20green%20signal%20to%20move%20ahead%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20group%20of%20farmers%20in%20a%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20young%20farmer%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20front%20near%20the%20Shambu%20border%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20the%20China%20or%20Pakistan%20border%20but%20look%20how%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20barricaded%20the%20entire%20border.%20We%20are%20not%20asking%20for%20anything%20unjust.%20It%20is%20our%20legitimate%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20for%20Delhi%20Chalo%20was%20given%20by%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%20and%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(non-political)%20led%20by%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20and%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%2C%20respectively%2C%20and%20other%20unions.%20Before%20leaving%20for%20Delhi%2C%20the%20farmers%20also%20held%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20BBC%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20laid%20multi-layered%20blocks%20at%20Singhu%2C%20Tikri%20and%20Ghazipur%20borders%2C%20which%20are%20the%20key%20intersections%20to%20reach%20Delhi%20on%20the%20road%20from%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana.%20The%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20also%20installed%20CCTV%20cameras%20at%20multiple%20locations%20at%20these%20three%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%202020%2C%20farmers%20had%20set%20up%20tents%20and%20parked%20their%20tractor-trailers%20at%20these%20borders%20for%20over%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20the%20Haryana%20police%E2%80%99s%20action%2C%20the%20Punjab%20Police%20was%20seen%20facilitating%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20march%20at%20various%20locations%20and%20ensured%20that%20both%20the%20farmers%20and%20other%20commuters%20did%20not%20face%20any%20difficulty.%20KMM%20coordinator%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20also%20managed%20the%20traffic.%20Standing%20on%20top%20of%20a%20moving%20vehicle%2C%20Pandher%20was%20seen%20addressing%20the%20farmers%20cavalcade.%20%E2%80%9CPlease%20maintain%20discipline%20and%20move%20in%20a%20line%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20kept%20repeating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20led%20by%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20Modi%20government%20for%20laying%20concertina%20wires%20and%20arranging%20drones%2C%20tear%20gas%2C%20nails%20and%20guns%20to%20counter%20the%20farmers.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20broken%20three%20promises%20which%20it%20had%20made%20to%20the%20farmers%3A%20doubling%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20by%202022%2C%20implementing%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20report%20and%20an%20MSP%20law.%20%E2%80%9CTime%20has%20come%20to%20raise%20voice%20for%2062%20crore%20farmers%20of%20the%20country.%20Congress%20will%20raise%20%E2%80%98Kisan%20Nyay%E2%80%99%20at%20Chattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Ambikapur%20today.%20We%20support%20farmers%20protest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20from%20the%20Punjab%20Congress%2C%20MLA%20Sukhpal%20Singh%20Khaira%20also%20went%20live%20on%20Facebook%20and%20announced%20that%20he%20will%20be%20proceeding%20towards%20the%20Shambu%20border%20to%20support%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20agitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20pictures%20of%20sealed%20borders%2C%20Khaira%20questioned%20whether%20this%20is%20how%20the%20government%20should%20treat%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20extreme%20cruelty%20with%20farmers%20who%20not%20only%20made%20India%20food%20sufficient%2C%20but%20remember%20its%20their%20sons%20who%20protect%20the%20borders%20in%20defence%20forces.%20Yet%20such%20barbarism%20against%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20too%20rejected%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20to%20convert%20Bawana%20Stadium%20into%20a%20temporary%20jail%20in%20view%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20Delhi%20Chalo%20march.%20Delhi%20government%20home%20minister%20Kailash%20Gahlot%20came%20out%20in%20support%20of%20the%20farmers%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20demands%20of%20the%20farmers%20are%20genuine.%20Secondly%2C%20it%20is%20the%20constitutional%20right%20of%20every%20citizen%20to%20peacefully%20protest.%20It%20is%20therefore%20incorrect%20to%20arrest%20the%20farmers.%20The%20Central%20government%20in%20fact%20should%20invite%20them%20over%20for%20talks%20and%20try%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20their%20genuine%20demands.%20Farmers%20of%20the%20country%20are%20our%20%3Cem%3Eannadata%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20treating%20them%20in%20this%20way%20by%20arresting%20them%20would%20be%20like%20rubbing%20salt%20into%20their%20wounds.%20We%20cannot%20be%20party%20to%20this%20decision.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20before%20beginning%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20march%2C%20KMM%20coordinator%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20and%20Bharti%20Kisan%20Union%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%20spokesperson%20Tejveer%20Singh%20Ambala%20held%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%2C%20Pandher%20said%20that%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20was%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20are%20acting%20as%20opposition%20in%20the%20country.%20Anybody%20including%20the%20senior%20farmer%20union%20leaders%20of%20SKM%2C%20who%20led%20the%20previous%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%2C%20are%20free%20to%20join%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejveer%20Ambala%20said%20that%20within%20one%20hour%20of%20the%20late-night%20meeting%2C%20they%20had%20realised%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20fulfilling%20their%20demands.%20%E2%80%9COur%20demand%20is%20an%20MSP%20guarantee%20law%2C%20justice%20for%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20victims%2C%20waiving%20off%20loans%20of%20the%20farmers%20and%20compensation%20to%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%20We%20will%20not%20return%20home%20without%20getting%20these%20demands%20fulfilled%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707814575000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13142417%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-2.14.07-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fpolice-use-tear-gas-on-protesting-farmers-at-punjab-haryana-border%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Farmers%20were%20breaking%20and%20removing%20barricades%20at%20the%20border%20when%20the%20police%20fired%20tear%20gas%20at%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fpolice-use-tear-gas-on-protesting-farmers-at-punjab-haryana-border%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20job%20cuts%3A%202%20words%20that%20rule%20most%20US%20firms%20earnings%20calls'%20transcripts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707813554000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107656330%2Cimgsize-63716.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fai-job-cuts-2-words-that-rule-most-us-companies-earnings-calls-transcripts%2Farticleshow%2F107655965.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20Armenian%20soldiers%20killed%20by%20Azerbaijani%20fire%20in%20first%20major%20incident%20since%20talks%20began%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707813271000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107656174%2Cimgsize-543112.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftwo-armenian-soldiers-killed-by-azerbaijani-fire-in-first-major-incident-since-talks-began%2Farticleshow%2F107655790.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220