klim-namun-minim-tindakan%5C%22%3EClimate%20Change%20Communication%20Center%20at%20Yale%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%202023%20of%203%2C490%20adults%20in%2034%20provinces%20showed%20that%20respondents%20prioritise%20environmental%20concerns%2C%20with%20water%20scarcity%20topping%20the%20list%20at%2091%20percent%2C%20storms%20or%20tornadoes%20(88%20percent)%2C%20droughts%20(87%20percent)%2C%20forest%20fires%20(86%20percent)%2C%20water%20pollution%20(85%20percent)%2C%20air%20pollution%20(83%20percent)%2C%20floods%20(83%20percent)%2C%20rising%20sea%20levels%20(77%20percent)%2C%20and%20extreme%20heat%20(69%20percent).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20there%20is%20strong%20interest%20in%20climate%20change%20among%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20younger%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20cannot%20be%20said%20of%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20politicians%20who%20%C2%A0have%20yet%20to%20make%20it%20a%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.monash.edu%2Findonesia%2Four-research%2Fmonash-climate-change-communication-research-hub-indonesia-node%2Fnews-article-mcccrh%2Fauthored-an-article-championing-climate-change-issue-in-the-indonesia-2024-election-campaign%5C%22%3EOur%20study%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20157%20Indonesian%20politicians%E2%80%99%20Facebook%20posts%20showed%20that%20politicians%20rarely%20talk%20%C2%A0about%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20from%202019%20to%202023%20on%20accounts%20belonging%20to%20ministers%2C%20governors%20and%20deputy%20governors%2C%20party%20chiefs%20and%2048%20heads%20and%20deputy%20heads%20of%20commission%20at%20the%20House%20of%20Representative%2C%20%C2%A0revealed%20106%20(out%20of%20983)%20had%20posted%20about%20climate%20change%20at%20least%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dominant%20topics%20from%20the%20analysis%20were%20global%20partnership%2C%20sustainable%20transportation%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20mangrove%20management%20and%20environmental%20conservation%2C%20and%20economic%20recovery%20after%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETopics%20that%20directly%20impact%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%20were%20talked%20about%20the%20least%20by%20Indonesian%20politicians.%20%C2%A0Agriculture%20and%20food%20security%2C%20the%20importance%20of%20clean%20water%2C%20extreme%20weather%20and%20climate%20change%20awareness%20made%20up%20just%20%C2%A0112%20posts%20or%2011.39%20percent%20of%20all%20posts.%20%C2%A0A%20mere%2018%20posts%20(1.83%20percent)%20related%20to%20youth%20involvement%20in%20climate%20change%20and%20environmental%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20494px)%2085vw%2C%20494px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13124105%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-12.40.49-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22494%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13124105%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-12.40.49-PM.png%201010w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13124105%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-12.40.49-PM-267x300.png%20267w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13124105%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-12.40.49-PM-910x1024.png%20910w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696897%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22555%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%202024%20Indonesia%20election%20is%20not%20a%20climate%20election%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20analysed%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Findonesia%2Fmedia-67425884%5C%22%3Eproposed%20vision%20and%20mission%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20the%20three%20candidates%20that%20they%20submitted%20to%20the%20election%20commission.%20None%20pay%20much%20attention%20to%20climate%20change%20and%20environmental%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20scanning%20the%20vision%20and%20mission%20documents%20of%20the%20three%20candidates%20for%20%C2%A0four%20keywords%20(%E2%80%9Cenvironment%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cclimate%E