6871%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22418%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20poster%20%E2%80%98welcoming%E2%80%99%20Shahjahan.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShahjahan%20Sheikh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20local%20said%20that%20rising%20awareness%20of%20how%20the%20state%20government%20is%20%E2%80%9Clooting%E2%80%9D%20people%E2%80%99s%20money%20is%20why%20internet%20has%20been%20shut%20down.%20%E2%80%9CYouth%20are%20able%20to%20look%20up%20how%20%3Cspan%3E%20Shahjahan%20Sheikh%20has%20claimed%20to%20have%20done%20work%20worth%20crores%20which%20have%20come%20to%20naught%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahjahan%20Sheikh%20is%20very%20much%20the%20centre%20of%20all%20things%20Sandeshkhali.%20It%20is%20to%20search%20his%20house%20that%20ED%20officials%20arrived%20in%20the%20village%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20public%20distribution%20system%20scam.%C2%A0%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20Shahjahan%E2%80%99s%20whereabouts%20have%20remained%20unknown%20despite%20multiple%20summons%20and%20a%20lookout%20notice%20by%20the%20ED.%20His%20legal%20team%20has%20sought%20court%20approval%20for%20bail%20on%20several%20occasions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDidi%20is%20protecting%20him.%20He%20is%20being%20sheltered%20by%20the%20police%20and%20the%20administration.%20They%20might%20want%20to%20diffuse%20the%20anger%20by%20arresting%20one%20or%20two%20people%2C%20but%20the%20main%20culprit%20is%20still%20at%20large%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20local%20woman%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Kacharipara%20part%20of%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20another%20villager%20says%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Efinancial%20corruption%20in%20the%20village%20%E2%80%9Cstarted%20soon%20after%20Trinamool%20came%20to%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYoung%20boys%20of%2015-16%20years%20were%20lured%20with%20alcohol.%20The%20biker%20gang%20of%20the%20party%20picked%20up%20our%20children%20from%20school%2C%20gave%20them%20guns%2C%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20take%20part%20in%20violence.%20The%20situation%20has%20worsened%20since%202018.%20They%20looted%20money%2C%20land%20and%20our%20women%E2%80%99s%20honour%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20villager%20claimed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolice%3A%20Arrests%2C%20re-arrests%20and%20no%20%E2%80%98rape%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20three%20being%20accused%20of%20such%20crimes%20%E2%80%93%20Shahjahan%2C%20Uttam%20Sardar%20and%20Sibu%20Hazra%20%E2%80%93%20are%20members%20of%20the%20TMC-run%20Zilla%20Parishad.%20While%20Uttam%20won%20uncontested%2C%20Shahjahan%20and%20Sibu%20received%2099.9%25%20and%2098%25%20of%20total%20votes%20in%20the%20latest%20panchayat%20polls.%20Many%20believe%20that%20such%20figures%20indicate%20irregularities%20in%20the%20voting%20process%20rather%20than%20the%20mass%20support%20they%20command.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFaced%20with%20massive%20outrage%20from%20across%20the%20state%2C%20TMC%20on%20February%2010%20suspended%20Uttam%20for%20six%20years.%20For%20locals%2C%20this%20is%20little%20more%20than%20a%20token%20gesture.%20While%20Uttam%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20soon%20after%20that%2C%20police%20also%20arrested%20former%20Sandeshkhali%20MLA%20and%20CPI(M)%20state%20committee%20member%20Nirapada%20Sardar%20on%20the%20afternoon%20of%20February%2011%2C%20from%20Kolkata%2C%20based%20on%20an%20FIR%20filed%20by%20Sibu%20who%20is%20still%20absconding.%20In%20the%20mean%20time%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20Bikash%20Sinha%20was%20also%20held.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20were%20produced%20in%20the%20Basirhat%20court%20a%20day%20ago.%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20Uttam%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Bikash%20got%20bail%2C%20but%20CPI(M)%20leader%20Nirapada%2C%20did%20not.%C2%A0%20BJP%20and%20TMC%20workers%C2%A0%20outside%20the%20court%2