pener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294472%2Fair-conditioner-ac-works-on-solar-panel-energy-reduce-electricity-bill%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20power%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20not%20in%20use.%20Further%20refinements%20were%20made%20to%20enhance%20the%20smooth%20processing%20and%20display%20of%20data%2C%20ultimately%20overcoming%20the%20initial%20challenges%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20from%20concept%20to%20the%20current%20prototype%20spanned%20four%20years.%20Through%20successive%20iterations%2C%20they%20have%20refined%20the%20device%2C%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20monitored%20water%20parameters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20current%20model%20represents%20the%20third%20prototype%20with%20plans%20to%20expand%20its%20capabilities%20further%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-IoT-Feature-1707316244.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IoT-enabled%20water%20quality%20measuring%20device%20in%20IIT-Guwahati%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-IoT-Feature-1707316244.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-IoT-Feature-1707316244-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-IoT-Feature-1707316244-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-IoT-Feature-1707316244-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-