firm%20was%20fraught%20with%20learning.%20The%20gamut%20of%20online%20frauds%20was%20many%2C%20Pratyusha%20discovered%20%E2%80%94%20credit%20card%20frauds%2C%20UPI%20frauds%2C%20refund%20frauds%2C%20spoofing%2C%20identity%20theft%2C%20scam%20pop-up%20alerts%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20raptorX.ai%E2%80%99s%20solution%20works%20on%20an%20algorithm%20where%20it%20assesses%20a%20website%E2%80%99s%20Alexa%20Rank%20(a%20reliable%20indicator%20to%20judge%20the%20website%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20based%20on%20the%20volume%20of%20website%20visitors%20in%20a%20given%20time%20frame).%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289824%2Fai-job-recruitment-portal-offers-free-registration-courses-mock-tests-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epopularity%20of%20a%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20a%20key%20indicator%20of%20how%20reliable%20it%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pratyusha.%20The%20next%20aspect%20is%20social%20media%20activity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CScam%20websites%20are%20often%20not%20too%20bothered%20by%20this%2C%20as%20it%20takes%20effort%20and%20resources%20to%20maintain%20social%20media%20pages.%20Therefore%20our%20algorithm%20can%20check%20if%20a%20site%20has%20active%20social%20media%20accounts%20and%20will%20adjust%20the%20score%20accordingly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20performance%20of%20a%20website%20is%20another%20parameter%20judged%20by%20raptorX.ai.%20%E2%80%9CScammers%20have%20sloppy%2C%20inefficient%20websites.%20Our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340832%2Fadvanced-stem-learning-helps-6000-students-in-govt-schools-innovate-thanks-to-one-initiative%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealgorithm%3C%2Fa%3E%20takes%20this%20into%20account%20and%20will%20reduce%20the%20score%20based%20on%20poor%20performance%20in%20this%20area.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20look%20at%20the%20security%20of%20the%20website%3B%20when%20the%20security%20cert%20was%20issued%20and%20when%20it%20expires%20along%20with%20any%20known%20malware%20on%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20goes%20on%20to%20add%20that%20certain%20markers%20suggest%20whether%20a%20business%20is%20genuine%20or%20not.%20These%20include%20transparent%20company%20data%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CGenuine%20businesses%20usually%20have%20nothing%20to%20hide%20and%20do%20not%20hide%20their%20company%20data%20from%20the%20registration%E2%80%9D%20and%20age%20of%20the%20website%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CScam%20sites%20are%20usually%20run%20as%20%E2%80%98hit-and-run%E2%80%99%20operations%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20site%20is%20created%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20being%20quickly%20shut%20down%20by%20the%20owners%20after%20scamming%20a%20lot%20of%20customers%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20time%2C%20the%20scope%20of%20raptorX.ai%E2%80%99s%20solutions%20is%20only%20set%20to%20increase%2C%20says%20Pratyusha.%20This%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20boom%20that%20the%20global%20Fraud%20Detection%20and%20Prevention%20(FDP)%20market%20is%20witnessing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCxsOXHaorRI%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCxsOXHaorRI%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%