usinesses%20can%20make%20better%20and%20innovative%20decisions%20on%20their%20products%20and%20increase%20top-line%20revenue%20and%20reduce%20customer%20churn.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrauds%20are%20very%20nuanced%20and%20industries%20need%20nuanced%20solutions%20to%20prevent%20frauds.%20It%20is%20even%20more%20critical%20in%20India%20and%20APAC%20as%20there%20are%20so%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296115%2Fteenagers-startup-finance4teens-educate-kids-globally-on-banking-financial-literacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emany%20businesses%3C%2Fa%3E%20coming%20online%20and%20they%20are%20exposed%20to%20more%20fraud%20than%20malware!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20service%20by%20raptorX.ai%20is%20the%20AI%20Kavach%20app%2C%20which%20scours%20a%20user%E2%80%99s%20phone%20when%20downloaded%20and%20points%20out%20scam%20messages%20and%20websites.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPratyusha%20calls%20it%20a%20one-stop%20solution%20to%20all%20cybersecurity%20qualms.%20%E2%80%9CA%20user%20can%20download%20the%20app%2C%20pay%20as%20low%20as%2099%20Rs%2Fyear%2C%20and%20give%20the%20necessary%20transparent%20permissions%20to%20detect%20fraud%20websites%20and%20messages%20real-time%20on%20the%20phone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20has%20been%20delisted%20for%20a%20few%20months%20based%20on%20Shark%20Tank%E2%80%99s%20feedback%20and%20will%20soon%20be%20available%20for%20download.%20The%20current%20focus%20is%20on%20scaling%20the%20B2B%20services.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Pratyusha%2C%20she%20is%20thrilled%20at%20the%20journey%20ahead.%20%E2%80%9CI%20took%20a%20problem%20and%20decided%20to%20channel%20my%20expertise%20to%20come%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F63836%2Fchetna-gala-sinha-mann-deshi-mahila-bank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20solution%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%